{"tid":856880,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人緣好差 可以點改善","createTime":"2018-10-10T23:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T03:09:03.000Z","uid":149689,"like":53,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2131a352c7b25f8ecb8e6ddf5265cfa0227f4aed","tid":856880,"uid":149689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:17:19.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好內向 好怕醜<br />\n識親既朋友都係人地做主動<br />\n久而久之就唔識點主動撩人講野<br />\n人大左就越黎越少朋友<br />\n開始覺得孤獨 <br />\n雖然身邊既朋友都會介紹其他朋友俾我識<br />\n但係唔知係咪我個樣生得太唔友善<br />\n好少人會有興趣同我做朋友<br />\n有時連望都唔望<br />\n好傷心難過<br />\n好羨慕嗰啲好有親和力既人<br />\n個個都會鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n晚晚訓教前又諗好多呢啲野<br />\n諗下自己有啲咩問題<br />\n係咪太靜 太cool 令人覺得唔易接近<br />\n諗到皮膚又差 又無精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前聽人講戴水晶會對改善人際關係有用<br />\n點知戴左咁耐都係咁<br />\n<br />\n我都想笑多啲 外向啲 講多啲野<br />\n但係有時對住啲唔熟既人真係唔知講咩好<br />\n<br />\n究竟我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a215600429b3577d1989ee3f05762644e3a2cf","tid":856880,"uid":79632,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:39:58.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名睇吓點改善"},{"pid":"0309da5df77c2bf8c9f0a740acc8835582ebbdf2","tid":856880,"uid":149689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58a215600429b3577d1989ee3f05762644e3a2cf","tid":856880,"uid":79632,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:39:58.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名睇吓點改善"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同是天涯淪落人"},{"pid":"b0af3af690dc561cf97cfb874e1badaa8b1770c6","tid":856880,"uid":79632,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0