"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b1c5cd59bc1927b08711f42ea84439b56a31564","tid":856880,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T00:16:21.000Z","msg":"講多d野咪改善到 載水晶邊得架 根本性格問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:39:34.000Z","msg":"冇話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:52:54.000Z","msg":"點解有啲人可以係咪都咁多野講 究竟係點做到"},{"pid":"84aa317ef42df02d5ea9dd99cc17d89bdbfa7b7b","tid":856880,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2131a352c7b25f8ecb8e6ddf5265cfa0227f4aed","tid":856880,"uid":149689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:17:19.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好內向 好怕醜<br />\n識親既朋友都係人地做主動<br />\n久而久之就唔識點主動撩人講野<br />\n人大左就越黎越少朋友<br />\n開始覺得孤獨 <br />\n雖然身邊既朋友都會介紹其他朋友俾我識<br />\n但係唔知係咪我個樣生得太唔友善<br />\n好少人會有興趣同我做朋友<br />\n有時連望都唔望<br />\n好傷心難過<br />\n好羨慕嗰啲好有親和力既人<br />\n個個都會鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n晚晚訓教前又諗好多呢啲野<br />\n諗下自己有啲咩問題<br />\n係咪太靜 太cool 令人覺得唔易接近<br />\n諗到皮膚又差 又無精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前聽人講戴水晶會對改善人際關係有用<br />\n點知戴左咁耐都係咁<br />\n<br />\n我都想笑多啲 外向啲 講多啲野<br />\n但係有時對住啲唔熟既人真係唔知講咩好<br />\n<br />\n究竟我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"落街打波自動叫3打3,做到已成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbd415fa02b5f1009806b3186d6acd01bcdb9d1","tid":856880,"uid":79632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c6c9be5623838c22eade64e854d59429770b140","tid":856880,"uid":149689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a0e3326c7df95c88056a311f7dabe104f3ab525","tid":856880,"uid":79632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b1c5cd59bc1927b08711f42ea84439b56